<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-10-27T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-10-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="605" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d605">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">760D.6115/10–2745: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Finland</hi> (<persName type="from"><hi rend="italic">Hulley</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Helsinki</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-10-27">October 27,
                                1945</date>.<lb/>[Received October 28—3:50 a.m.]</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>641. Press 27th. New Petsamo border which exactly same as between Russian
                            Empire and Grand Duchy of Finland has been delineated and documents
                            reestablishing it signed Helsinki 26th.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Hulley</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>